ygData.messageBody:
nah, tried it last night...could not see invis party members, or other invis
people. Also, stuff that was formerly affected by invis seemed unaffected
after the patch (gorge hounds in EK, blue to me, used to not see through
invis, now they do). possibly they just nerfed the song, while saying they
enhanced it, dunno.

MacGrough Mich'rathe
20th Song bard
Solusek Ro Wanderers
